summary: Dit kan je vanaf november bij Videoland gaan kijken
title: Dit kan je vanaf november bij Videoland gaan kijken
body:
Er komen een hoop nieuwe serie en films naar de Nederlandse on demand dienst, dit is vanaf november bij Videoland te zien

Op on demand gebied blijven Netflix en Videoland in Nederland de grote spelers. Maar wat komt er de komende maand uit op de Nederlandse on demand dienst? hieronder heb ik een aantal grote titels voor je op een rij gezet. Van films tot series er is genoeg te zien in november…

summary:
You guys know what just gets me about this whole show? Delivery. 
When the KE-trailer came out ages ago, I was listening to this...
body:
You guys know what just gets me about this whole show? Delivery.

When the KE-trailer came out ages ago, I was listening to this monologue very intently and going all dayummm guurl you got it baaad. Then episode 08 rolled around I sat there muttering to myself like goddammit crap crap crap she still hasn’t said that stuff out loud oh we’re not gonna get it, too good to be true, we can’t have nice things, but then she did it and I swear I’m still like

summary: It is weird watching Killing Eve with my parents and they are not mentioning anything about the sexuality of the serial killer....
body: It is weird watching Killing Eve with my parents and they are not mentioning anything about the sexuality of the serial killer. Like there have been shots of threesomes having happened, various lesbian/bi/whatever kisses and obsession over another woman. Nope all my dad is weirded out by is a guy getting killed in a kinky way.
